The first line is the breadName of max 50 characters (truncated to 50 if length of breadName > 50).
Followed by maximum 10 lines of Sourdough Instructions in this format : “functionName  hh:mm:ss” or “functionName Option” where: 
“functioName” is one of the following functions or options n the Sourdough process (case insensitive):
Colour or Color, Knead, Drop, Degas, Proof, Rest, Bake.
If functionName is Knead, Degas, Proof, Rest or Bake, it must be followed by “hh:mm:ss”  which is Time in hours, minutes and seconds.
If functionName is Drop, it must not be followed by anything. 
if functionName is Colour or Color, it must be followed by the option  Light, Medium or Dark.

